# demo-injection.tape — AI Agent Injection Attack Demo
# Records: attack → agent hijacked → /security catches it → fixed
# Output: demo-injection.gif

Output demo-injection.gif

Require echo

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 20

Type "bash scripts/demo-injection.sh"
Enter
Sleep 30s
